### Banking Transactions API — Sample Requests
### Compatible with VS Code REST Client and JetBrains HTTP Client

@base = http://localhost:3000

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Task 1: Core CRUD
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Create a deposit
POST {{base}}/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "toAccount": "ACC-12345",
  "amount": 1000.00,
  "currency": "USD",
  "type": "deposit"
}

###

### Create a transfer
POST {{base}}/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromAccount": "ACC-12345",
  "toAccount": "ACC-67890",
  "amount": 250.00,
  "currency": "USD",
  "type": "transfer"
}

###

### Create a withdrawal
POST {{base}}/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromAccount": "ACC-12345",
  "amount": 75.50,
  "currency": "USD",
  "type": "withdrawal"
}

###

### List all transactions
GET {{base}}/transactions

###

### Get a single transaction (replace <id> with a real ID)
# GET {{base}}/transactions/<id>

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Task 2: Validation errors
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Invalid: negative amount
POST {{base}}/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "toAccount": "ACC-12345",
  "amount": -10,
  "currency": "USD",
  "type": "deposit"
}

###

### Invalid: bad currency
POST {{base}}/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "toAccount": "ACC-12345",
  "amount": 100,
  "currency": "XYZ",
  "type": "deposit"
}

###

### Invalid: bad account format
POST {{base}}/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "toAccount": "12345",
  "amount": 100,
  "currency": "USD",
  "type": "deposit"
}

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Task 3: Filters
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

###

### Filter by account
GET {{base}}/transactions?accountId=ACC-12345

###

### Filter by type
GET {{base}}/transactions?type=deposit

###

### Filter by date range
GET {{base}}/transactions?from=2024-01-01&to=2024-12-31

###

### Combined filters
GET {{base}}/transactions?accountId=ACC-12345&type=transfer

###

### Account balance
GET {{base}}/accounts/ACC-12345/balance

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Task 4: CSV Export
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

###

### Export all as CSV
GET {{base}}/transactions/export?format=csv

###

### Export filtered by account
GET {{base}}/transactions/export?format=csv&accountId=ACC-12345
